    Interface Description
    BoundCipherInterface
    The interface implemented by bi-directional ciphers that use a bound key.

    The interface implemented by ciphers that decrypt data and use a bound key.

    The interface implemented by ciphers that encrypt data and use a bound key.

    The interface implemented by Lockbox bi-directional ciphers.
    DecryptionCipherInterface

    EncryptionCipherInterface
    The interface implemented by Lockbox encryption ciphers.
